==================================================================
Prerequisites
==================================================================

1. Make sure you have the Qt SDK installed and working.

==================================================================
Building
==================================================================

From the command line, in the root directory, run the following
commands:

1. cd dev
2. qmake
3. make

Alternatively, use QtCreator and build the application from the IDE.

==================================================================
Installing
==================================================================

-Windows-
Use windeployqt in the \bin directory to package necessary dlls.
The directory is self-contained and can be zipped and distributed.
The user must install the appropriate MSVC runtime.


-Linux-
Simply run the executable.
